title: 3DMark Vantage + Keymaker - CORE
description:
This is the original 3DMark Vantage uploaded by loder. I just removed the 95 archives and put it into one single .rar file.


System Requirements:



Windows Vista Service Pack 1

Dual Core processor equal to Intel Core 2 Duo E6600 or AMD Athlon 64 X2 6000+

DirectX 10 compatible graphics card

2 GB Ram is recommended

1 GB harddrive space


Hope you enjoy this!
